rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, how's tricks? Been putting
that Perfect Range Sensor I gave
you to good use?

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Me? I've been out and about hiking
all over Alst.

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm studying flora from all over the
world, see. And I'm learning more
and more by the day!

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I finished the first leg of my journey,
so I'm catching a bit of R&R back at
the old homestead for now.

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Field research's ace, but it's writing up
the research paper that I'm dreading...

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Well, I'll scrape something together
somehow.
